Name of usecase represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor Clicks [*Inventory*|guide:_showInventoryPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Report" sub menu from left menu.
* Click "Item Reconciliation" link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Item Reconciliation" Report|guide:ShowForItemReconciliationActionService].
* User must insert valid input.
* Click "CSV" icon upper right side of the page.
* System will show confirmation message of download.
* Actor clicks "Ok" button.
* Download "Item Reconciliation" Report in CSV Format.

h4. Pre-condition: 
* User must have "Download Item Reconciliation Csv Report" privilege.
* Rules of searching field:
{table}
 *Field* | *Input Type* | *Data Type* | *Rules* 
 [Populate Project List|application] | Drop-Down List | Numeric | Default(All)
{table}


h4. Process:
* Downloaded CSV Report is same as grid report.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** CSV Report will successfully download to user's computer.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].
